<br>
Frak and Lath I wish you could have stayed, but I know it was REAL late.  I still can't believe Harlan did not fall asleep at his keys!<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  We did not celebrate and log until 4am Pacific Time!<br>
<br>
