<br>
It was awesome to be there for the first part anyways, though we need to have better planning for the next one, especially once inside. Like assigning groups specifically to cover the archer respawns on the walls and makeing sure that more than one group has ram materials. (I wonder if you can double up on the rams at the keep doors?) <br>
