<br>
Supposedly we get a 5% melee bonus in RvR by having this relic (not much I know, but the entire realm gets it).  The next relic we attempt will be a magic one.<br>
<br>
There was no resistence taking the relic back...  We lost people to guards and mobs tho, so it wasn't a cakewalk.  If the relic carrier was killed the relic would instantly port back to the relic keep.<br>
<br>
Their relic is now at excalibur, right next to ours.  That means we can expect Mid to try to take it back, and you KNOW those freaking Hibs are salavating at the chance to pick up 2 relics in one raid!  We are now THE prime target (as if we weren't before?  Heh).<br>
